10
00:02:56,609 --> 00:02:58,941
It wasn't the Colonel, but it
was a chicken stand nevertheless.

11
00:02:59,012 --> 00:03:01,981
And I pulled the Mercury
right up alongside

12
00:03:02,048 --> 00:03:05,484
and I rolled down the window,
see, by electric power.

13
00:03:05,552 --> 00:03:09,716
And she had this leather skirt on.

14
00:03:09,789 --> 00:03:12,781
And she had a lot of hair on her arms.

15
00:03:12,859 --> 00:03:18,855
I like hair, I like hair a lot. It
means a big bush. I like a big bush.

16
00:03:19,732 --> 00:03:24,829
So she says, "Are you dating?" You know?

17
00:03:24,904 --> 00:03:27,099
I said, "Sure." So she gets in.

18
00:03:27,173 --> 00:03:32,440
And we pull off into this
remote location, you know,

19
00:03:32,512 --> 00:03:34,776
that was comfortable for both she and I.

20
00:03:34,847 --> 00:03:38,214
And she says to me, "How
much do you wanna spend?"

21
00:03:38,284 --> 00:03:41,913
And I said, "Whatever it takes to see that
bush of yours, 'cause I know it's a big one."

22
00:03:41,988 --> 00:03:44,980
And she says to me, "25 dollars."

23
00:03:47,093 --> 00:03:52,030
That's not chicken feed,
you know... to a working man.

24
00:03:52,098 --> 00:03:57,434
So I produce the 25 dollars and she sticks
it down into her shoe and pulls up her skirt.

25
00:03:57,503 --> 00:04:00,904
And there before me lay this thin,

26
00:04:00,974 --> 00:04:03,966
crooked, uncircumcised penis.

27
00:04:09,182 --> 00:04:13,585
You can imagine how bad I
wanted my 25 dollars back, huh?

28
00:04:17,123 --> 00:04:20,718
("Girl) I don't know why you're so
weirded out. This is not San Quentin.

29
00:04:20,793 --> 00:04:23,489
